      <title>干旱点上纳米比亚争斗中的动物的人类食物</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/human-wildlife-conflict-in-namibia-worsens-amid-severe-drought</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五发表的一份议会报告称，纳米比亚的人类与野生动物之间的冲突正在升级，因为严重的干旱加剧了农村地区的食物和水的竞争，而且该问题因过时的政策而加剧了问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/human-wildlife-conflict-in-namibia-worsens-amid-severe-drought</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 14:42:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
